column5: Went digging thru some stuff to see what to throw out and ran across some old fesh pictures, posted them on my myspace page you can check them out there if you would like? Mostly Lake Erie fish but some GB and farm ponds.  Paul Dillon
Myspace? What's that  It's all about Facebook man, then again it would be nice to have celebrities and rockstars as friends on that other place lol
I thought facebook was for girls? LOL Mike you don`t think I am going thru the trouble of putting them on both? I am retired and that is work? Go fish kid while you still have legs! LOL
lol, in the river, at this time of the season...lol
LOL Mike i was usually March for me, 16 years old and catch bait to sell for gas money. Shorts and tennis shoes, didn`t need jeans my legs turned blue.
